---
---

<section id="about" class="bg-brutal-black py-20 px-6" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <!-- Section counter -->
    <div class="text-brutal-grey text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 reveal">/01</div>
    <h2 id="about-heading" class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brutal-white uppercase tracking-tight mb-16 reveal">
      About
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
      <!-- Photo placeholder -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-4 reveal">
        <div class="border border-brutal-rule aspect-square flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden">
          <span class="text-[8rem] font-bold text-brutal-rule/20 select-none">K</span>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-brutal-red"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-8 reveal">
        <p class="text-brutal-white/80 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Hi there! I'm passionate about solving real-world problems through programming and coding. Whether I'm diving into complex challenges or experimenting with new CLI tools, I love finding creative solutions to hard problems. Of course that means I use vim for my day to day coding and file editing.
        </p>

        <p class="text-brutal-white/80 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          I'm also on a journey to hone my technical writing and design skills. I believe that clear communication and well-crafted design are just as important as the code itself&mdash;they help transform complex ideas into accessible solutions.
        </p>

        <p class="text-brutal-white/80 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          I'm always eager to connect with businesses and individuals who need a fresh perspective or innovative technical solutions. If you think my approach could be a good fit for your project or venture, let's start a conversation.
        </p>

        <!-- Tech stack grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="brutal-card !p-4 text-center">
            <div class="text-brutal-red text-2xl font-bold mb-1">FE</div>
            <div class="text-brutal-grey text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">React / Astro</div>
          </div>
          <div class="brutal-card !p-4 text-center">
            <div class="text-brutal-red text-2xl font-bold mb-1">BE</div>
            <div class="text-brutal-grey text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Node / Spring</div>
          </div>
          <div class="brutal-card !p-4 text-center">
            <div class="text-brutal-red text-2xl font-bold mb-1">TS</div>
            <div class="text-brutal-grey text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">TypeScript</div>
          </div>
          <div class="brutal-card !p-4 text-center">
            <div class="text-brutal-red text-2xl font-bold mb-1">DB</div>
            <div class="text-brutal-grey text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">SQL / NoSQL</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Social links (text-based) -->
        <nav aria-label="Social media links" class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">
          <a href="https://github.com/Kameleon21" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-brutal-grey hover:text-brutal-red transition-colors">GitHub &rarr;</a>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kamil-rogozinski/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-brutal-grey hover:text-brutal-red transition-colors">LinkedIn &rarr;</a>
          <a href="https://x.com/KamilRogozinski" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-brutal-grey hover:text-brutal-red transition-colors">X / Twitter &rarr;</a>
          <a href="mailto:kamilrogozinski29@gmail.com"
            class="text-brutal-grey hover:text-brutal-red transition-colors">Email &rarr;</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
